{"data":[{"date":"23:35 08/08","title":"C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A CHINH TH\u1ee8C \u0111\u1ed5i sang logo m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu si\u00eau sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A m\u00f9a n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n khi chia tay logo c\u0169 sang th\u00e0nh m\u1eabu m\u1edbi mang h\u01a1i h\u01b0\u1edbng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n.</h2><h2>Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean Serie A nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn ngh\u0129. L\u00e0n s\u00f3ng b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh khi Serie A h\u00e8 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng sau Premier League v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00e1c CLB b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo nh\u1eb1m t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, Serie A c\u0169ng l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh theo ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c g\u00f3i ba n\u0103m gi\u1ed1ng Premier League. \u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n vi\u1ec7c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo m\u1edbi theo h\u01a1i h\u01b0\u1edbng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n, nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o ch\u1eef \"A\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Serie A c\u0169ng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u00e1c trang m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i m\u1edbi tr\u00ean Facebook, Instagram v\u00e0 Twitter, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t t\u00ean \"SerieA\". Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng h\u01a1n h\u01a1n 1.2 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i logo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch Serie A t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \"xu\u1ed1ng gi\u00e1\". Ch\u1eef A trong logo m\u1edbi c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \"Appassionante, Avvincente, Adrenalinica\" - t\u1ea1m d\u1ecbch \"th\u00fa v\u1ecb, h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, b\u01a1m Adrenaline\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Logo cu cua Serie A.\" title=\"Logo c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Serie A.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/serie-a-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Logo c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Serie A.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBan \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Serie A k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng logo m\u1edbi b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb \"khao kh\u00e1t t\u1ea1o n\u00ean t\u00ednh trung t\u00e2m cho ch\u1eef A\", c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \"m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta\". Vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i logo Serie A c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i Italia nh\u01b0 Coppa Italia, Si\u00eau C\u00fap Italia v\u00e0 Primavera.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"M\u1ed9t c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn m\u1edbi, t\u1ea1o ra t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ef1c quan, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n g\u1ed3m l\u00e1 c\u1edd Italia, m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u1eef A, t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb s\u1ef1 v\u1eefng b\u1ec1n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi TIM\" - Tr\u00edch t\u1eeb th\u00f4ng c\u00e1o b\u00e1o ch\u00ed.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Serie A 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-nhan-xet-cristiano-ronaldo-den-serie-a-176-193919.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 ho\u00e0ng kim c\u1ee7a Serie A</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muc-luong-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-o-juventus-khung-khiep-den-the-nao-176-193834.html\">M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf Juventus kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/liverpool-vs-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-372-193724.html\">Liverpool 5-0 Napoli: The Klopp h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Serie A trong ng\u00e0y Alisson ra m\u1eaft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muc-tieu-cua-chelsea-dong-y-o-lai-serie-a-176-192603.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-khi-sao-serie-a-la-mieng-pizza-trong-mat-cac-dai-gia-nha-172-192560.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Khi sao Serie A l\u00e0 mi\u1ebfng pizza trong m\u1eaft c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia NHA</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/sieu-sao-ronaldo-giup-juventus-pha-ky-luc-tren-youtube-188-192551.html\">Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo gi\u00fap Juventus ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c tr\u00ean YouTube</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2147","checkdouble":"194058"},{"date":"00:05 09/08","title":"Paul Scholes ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man Utd m\u00f9a n\u00e0y k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/paul-scholes-che-doi-hinh-man-utd-mua-nay-kem-chat-luong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Paul Scholes kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Manchester United, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 HLV Jose Mourinho nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>Paul Scholes ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man Utd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Jose Mourinho, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Man Utd hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Wayne Rooney cho r\u1eb1ng Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Scholes che doi hinh Man Utd mua nay kem chat luong.\" title=\"Paul Scholes ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man Utd m\u00f9a n\u00e0y k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/paul-scholes-che-doi-hinh-man-utd-mua-nay-kem-chat-luong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Paul Scholes ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man Utd m\u00f9a n\u00e0y k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp h\u01a1n, Paul Scholes ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man Utd kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7: &quot;Khi nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o Man City hay Liverpool, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Man Utd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ed1t&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Man Utd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ng\u1eafn kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Man City. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i th\u00ec ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft r\u1ed3i, c\u00f2n Man Utd th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng ai bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn. Hy v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 t\u00f4i sai nh\u01b0ng Man Utd kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a n\u00e0y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, HLV Jose Mourinho v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a gi\u00fap Man Utd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a &quot;qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&quot; b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n khi ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ec1u cao c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Scholes cung cho rang Jose Mourinho co nguy co bi sa thai trong mua nay.\" title=\"Paul Scholes c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i trong m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/mourinho-13.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Paul Scholes c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i trong m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i \u1edf Anh \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Jose Mourinho l\u00e0 HLV c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Paul Scholes c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 Mourinho: &quot;Kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i. N\u1ebfu Man Utd ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng mang t\u00ednh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i&quot;.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Man Utd m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-88-man-utd-can-them-2-tan-binh-184-194054.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 8/8: Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-pogba-co-the-da-trung-ve-172-194003.html\">Mourinho: Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1... trung v\u1ec7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/mu-may-nhat-liverpool-xui-nhat-ngoai-hang-anh-mua-truoc-188-193943.html\">M.U may nh\u1ea5t, Liverpool xui nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giai-thich-ly-do-marcus-rashford-mang-ao-so-10-cua-man-utd-172-193910.html\">Mourinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-man-utd-chinh-thuc-tim-ra-tan-chu-nhan-cho-ao-so-10-172-193824.html\">N\u00f3ng! Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u00ecm ra t\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n cho \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hang-hot-world-cup-tiep-tuc-tha-thinh-man-utd-172-193822.html\">H\u00e0ng hot World Cup ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh Man Utd</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2146","checkdouble":"194059"},{"date":"00:37 09/08","title":"Sao HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/sao-hagl-noi-gi-khi-bi-loai-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 71.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><h2>Kepa gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Bilbao \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 7 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 71.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-chelsea-don-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-athletic-bilbao-xac-nhan-kepa-arrizabalaga-sap-den-chelsea-172-194052.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kepa \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge</span> \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho Thibaut Courtois, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Premier League trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat t\u00f4i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u00e0 Premier League. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00f4i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Chelsea n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Kepa</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge khi Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i quay l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Hai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Sarri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Kepa ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddersfield s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. D\u1eabu sao, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n lo l\u1eafng khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 Caballero \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Marina Granovskaia kh\u00e1 h\u00e2n hoan v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 Chelsea v\u1eeba th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cKepa l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea7n kh\u00edch khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Kepa \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o m\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eeba k\u00fd v\u1edbi Kepa th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB\u00a0Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mateo-kovacic-sap-den-chelsea-172-194055.html\">Ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ea5t Courtois, Chelsea s\u1eafp \u0111\u00f3n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/david-luiz-ung-ho-chelsea-mua-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194049.html\">Chelsea chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c mua Kepa, David Luiz n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2145","checkdouble":"194060"},{"date":"05:53 09/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 9/8: Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-sang-ngay-98-chelsea-lap-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 9/8.</h2><h2>Everton l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Everton \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho ng\u00f4i sao b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng t\u1ea1i Barca hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Andre Gomes. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Everton c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Andre Gomes thay v\u00ec mua \u0111\u1ee9t nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa v\u1edbi ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa\" title=\"Kepa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/3.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng 9/8: Kepa ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kepa gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho Courtois. M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 The Blues ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 cho Athletic Bilbao l\u00e0 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, t\u1ee9c kho\u1ea3ng 72 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Kepa \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua con s\u1ed1 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Alisson \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c l\u1eadp c\u0169ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Schalke ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn sao Tottenham</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Rose \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Schalke thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 Bundesliga m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y 31/8 v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho Schalke trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Spurs.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Boateng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Sky Sports \u0111\u01b0a tin HLV Jose Mourinho mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n s\u1eed ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i trong v\u00e0i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t giao k\u00e8o mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Man United b\u1ecb h\u1edb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Vida</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Evening Standard cho bi\u1ebft Arsenal \u0111ang quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 n\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng hay kh\u00f4ng. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Danny Welbeck t\u1edbi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 nh\u1eb1m gi\u1ea3m s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda Besiktas ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia. Vida \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mong mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Premier League. Nh\u01b0ng Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-88-man-utd-can-them-2-tan-binh-184-194054.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 8/8: Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-88-pogba-nang-nac-doi-roi-mu-184-193992.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 8/8: Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2144","checkdouble":"194063"},{"date":"06:11 09/08","title":"C\u1ef1u sao Liverpool d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Lovren t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/4/lovren-nhm-ung-ho-toi-nhieu-hon-modric-va-kovacic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Dirk Kuyt kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh trung v\u1ec7 Lovren \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Liverpool m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Kuyt \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Lovren</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Lovren trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m cho nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1ea1i Anfield. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi gi\u00fap Liverpool l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League, Lovren c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Croatia v\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. Sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/lovren-moi-nguoi-can-nhan-ra-chung-toi-la-nhung-nguoi-gioi-nhat-421-191045.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lovren \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1u sao Liverpool d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 Lovren t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u sao Liverpool d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 Lovren t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/4/lovren-nhm-ung-ho-toi-nhieu-hon-modric-va-kovacic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kuyt d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 Lovren s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Kuyt tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V Liverpool s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/dejan-lovren-44909.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lovren</span> \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cLovren l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch khi xem Croatia thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup. H\u1ecd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 gi\u00e2y. Croatia x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Croatia r\u1ed3i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Kuyt d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Liverpool s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kuyt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Feyenoord gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c V\u0110QG H\u00e0 Lan m\u00f9a 2016/17. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau g\u1ea7n 2 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 Kuyt tin r\u1eb1ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Liverpool ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t c\u01a1n kh\u00e1t Premier League khi \u0111\u00e3 chi ti\u00eau kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh tay \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cV\u1edbi Feyenoord, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u sau 18 n\u0103m. T\u00f4i tin Liverpool s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 sau 29 n\u0103m v\u00e0 Lovren s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e0y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 Van Dijk s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB\u00a0Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chi-co-bong-dang-cua-nha-vo-dich-sau-khi-chieu-mo-alisson-172-194000.html\">Liverpool ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch sau khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-thua-nhan-liverpool-chot-so-chuyen-nhuong-172-193996.html\">Klopp th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Liverpool ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2143","checkdouble":"194064"},{"date":"06:33 09/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea k\u00edch n\u1ed5 \"bom t\u1ea5n\" th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-chelsea-don-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 71.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><h2>Kepa gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Bilbao \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 7 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 71.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-chelsea-don-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-athletic-bilbao-xac-nhan-kepa-arrizabalaga-sap-den-chelsea-172-194052.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kepa \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge</span> \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho Thibaut Courtois, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Premier League trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat t\u00f4i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u00e0 Premier League. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00f4i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Chelsea n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Kepa</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge khi Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i quay l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Hai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Sarri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Kepa ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddersfield s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. D\u1eabu sao, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n lo l\u1eafng khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 Caballero \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Marina Granovskaia kh\u00e1 h\u00e2n hoan v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 Chelsea v\u1eeba th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cKepa l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea7n kh\u00edch khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Kepa \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o m\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eeba k\u00fd v\u1edbi Kepa th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB\u00a0Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mateo-kovacic-sap-den-chelsea-172-194055.html\">Ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ea5t Courtois, Chelsea s\u1eafp \u0111\u00f3n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/david-luiz-ung-ho-chelsea-mua-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194049.html\">Chelsea chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c mua Kepa, David Luiz n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2142","checkdouble":"194065"},{"date":"06:21 09/08","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (9/8/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-982018.jpg","n