a Gama (Brazil) - LDU Quito (Ecuador)</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2141","checkdouble":"194066"},{"date":"06:33 09/08","title":"Real Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 vi\u1ec7c mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Los Blancos theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2>Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid nh\u01b0 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\nTr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 CLB, c\u1ea3 Real Madrid l\u1eabn Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Thibaut Courtois. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng nay theo gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu c\u00f9ng ng\u00e0y. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic c\u0169ng s\u1ebd sang Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ngay sau khi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois xong xu\u00f4i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Chelsea v\u00e0 Real Madrid t\u1ed1i nay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Thibaut Courtois sau khi th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf. Sau khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh, Mateo Kovacic s\u1ebd sang The Blues theo d\u1ea1ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i\", Chelsea th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cReal Madrid C.F v\u00e0 Chelsea F.C \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 k\u00ed h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB 6 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Sau bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1 gi\u1edd chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 9/8 \u1edf SV\u0110 Santiago Bernabeu\u201d.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid sau khi r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid sau khi r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Thu-mon-Courtois-chinh-thuc-den-Real-Madrid-sau-khi-roi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Courtois c\u0169ng th\u1ecfa \u01b0\u1edbc nguy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Real. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \"ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n\" 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 \u00fd r\u1eddi The Blues, t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \"n\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1n\" n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Courtois khi\u1ebfn anh nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ti\u1ec1n 2 tu\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1edf d\u0129 Chelsea nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf  h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Kepa Arrizabalaga t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecf ra 72  tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Kepa v\u1ec1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, qua \u0111\u00f3  gi\u00fap anh v\u01b0\u1ee3t Alisson Becker (Liverpool) tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t  th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi The Blues ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn nhanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1n gi\u1ea5y m\u1ef1c b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCourtois gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Genk v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2011 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 9 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ea3i qua 3 m\u00f9a li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp (2011-2014) thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Atletico Madrid theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. T\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2014-15, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 The Blues thay Petr Cech (sang Arsenal), ra s\u00e2n 154 tr\u1eadn, gi\u00e0nh 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, 1 FA Cup c\u00f9ng 1 C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n.\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea h\u00e8 2018\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mateo-kovacic-sap-den-chelsea-172-194055.html\">Ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ea5t Courtois, Chelsea s\u1eafp \u0111\u00f3n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/david-luiz-ung-ho-chelsea-mua-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194049.html\">Chelsea chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c mua Kepa, David Luiz n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lo-dau-hieu-cho-thay-kovacic-sap-cap-ben-chelsea-172-194048.html\">L\u1ed9 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Kovacic s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/kepa-arrizabalaga-co-du-kha-nang-thay-the-vi-tri-do-courtois-de-lai-172-194047.html\">Kepa Arrizabalaga \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Courtois?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-va-giroud-muon-chelsea-mua-nabil-fekir-172-194029.html\">Hazard v\u00e0 Giroud mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2140","checkdouble":"194067"},{"date":"06:53 09/08","title":"Loay hoay t\u00ecm trung v\u1ec7, Mourinho t\u00ednh r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/loay-hoay-tim-trung-ve-mourinho-tinh-rut-ruot-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United \u0111ang t\u00ednh to\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Kurt Zouma c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Mourinho th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t.</h2><h2>MU nh\u1eafm Zouma</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Man United ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Zouma \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c. B\u1edfi The Blues kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc h\u1ecd c\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nZouma kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Stoke. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi The Potters \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Loay hoay t\u00ecm trung v\u1ec7, Mourinho t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Zouma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Loay hoay t\u00ecm trung v\u1ec7, Mourinho t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Zouma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/loay-hoay-tim-trung-ve-mourinho-tinh-rut-ruot-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kurt Zouma b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0a Zouma v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a Chelsea n\u0103m 2014. V\u00e0 t\u1edd L\u2019Equipe \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, MU s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Everton. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Zouma theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f2n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf mu\u1ed1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Chelsea t\u1eebng b\u00e1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho Man United. Mourinho t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea9y Mata \u0111\u1ebfn Man United n\u0103m 2014 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Nemanja Matic c\u0169ng m\u1edbi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Mourinho \u1edf United h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c mua trung v\u1ec7</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Zouma ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn sau khi Man United kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Toby Alderweireld v\u00e0 Harry Maguire nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng do ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn. Jerome Boateng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i Premier League s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay. V\u00e0 Man United ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t \u00edt th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-jerome-boateng-khong-phai-lua-chon-hoan-hao-voi-mu-172-194042.html\">V\u00ec sao Jerome Boateng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi MU?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-barca-thay-the-luke-shaw-172-194037.html\">MU nh\u1eafm sao Barca thay th\u1ebf Luke Shaw</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/bayern-khong-muon-mua-ante-rebic-193-194033.html\">M.U \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng trong v\u1ee5 s\u0103n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2139","checkdouble":"194068"},{"date":"06:55 09/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Premier League h\u00e8 2018 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda (9/8)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/9/chuyen-nhuong-premier-league-ngay-dong-cua.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c, tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Premier League h\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (9/8). Cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3ng, c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda TTCN Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh h\u00e8 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>* Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Premir League h\u00e8 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o l\u00fac 23h00 ng\u00e0y 9/8 (theo gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam)</strong><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00c1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thibaut Courtois m\u00e0 Real Madrid m\u1edbi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Real v\u1eabn coi Kovacic l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00ean ch\u1ec9 cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t anh. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng, Luka Modric \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nKovacic gia nh\u1eadp Real v\u00e0o h\u00e8 2015 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kho\u1ea3ng 29 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 c\u00f3 109 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 &ldquo;k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5&rdquo; v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i sau khi World Cup kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic se khoac ao Chelsea mua 2018-19\" title=\"Kovacic s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea m\u00f9a 2018-19\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/180809_054945_649.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kovacic s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea m\u00f9a 2018-19</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>T\u1ed4NG QUAN TTCN PREMIER LEAGUE NG\u00c0Y \u0110\u00d3NG C\u1eecA</h2>\r\nN\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, c\u00e1c CLB Premier League \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8. Theo \u0111\u00f3, thay v\u00ec k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 31/8 nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng l\u1ec7 th\u00ec b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb n\u0103m nay, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi sau ng\u00e0y 9/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Premier League h\u00e8 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 5 c\u1ee7a tu\u1ea7n khai m\u1ea1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u (gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng), t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi 23h00 ng\u00e0y 9/8 theo gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c CLB v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 (mua ho\u1eb7c m\u01b0\u1ee3n) n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edf c\u1eeda l\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y 1/1/2019. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 sau ng\u00e0y 9/8 v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00ec thu\u1ed9c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a UEFA.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 trong n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 Premier League. C\u00e1c CLB v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n ho\u1eb7c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sang c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c cho \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 31/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2138","checkdouble":"194069"},{"date":"15:44 08/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! Chi ti\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Courtois s\u1eafp k\u00fd v\u1edbi Real Madrid?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/day-chi-tiet-hop-dong-courtois-sap-ky-voi-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real Madrid nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 Kristof Terreur.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Courtois s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u1ecfi mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng qua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Thibaut-Courtois-ky-hop-dong-6-nam-voi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Real v\u1eabn \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Courtois \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng The Blues, anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u1edf B\u1ec9 trong khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Hazard, Giroud hay Kante \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Courtois c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1ea3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real Madrid nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 Kristof Terreur. \u00d4ng vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Twitter:&ldquo;Courtois \u0111ang \u1edf B\u1ec9, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Real Madrid&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Real s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Courtois v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Real k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Courtois v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111ang tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef Courtois \u1edf l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992. Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Jan Oblak, song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i The Blues \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e2y! Chi ti\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Courtois s\u1eafp k\u00fd v\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2y! Chi ti\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Courtois s\u1eafp k\u00fd v\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Day!-Chi-tiet-hop-dong-Courtois-sap-ky-voi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea nh\u1eafm Kepa thay Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga-172-193949.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa Arrizabalaga </span>c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi Bilbao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois, HLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;T\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 sau khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea3&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKepa Arrizabalaga khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 Chelsea th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Courtois, kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft g\u00ec c\u1ea3. C\u00f2n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin g\u00ec t\u1eeb BL\u0110 Bilbao&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2137","checkdouble":"194030"},{"date":"15:31 08/08","title":"Sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/dembele-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a tin ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn t\u1eeb Arsenal v\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barcelona th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00e1 t\u1ec7 t\u1ea1i Camp Nou. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 135.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng Dembele thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/dembele-muon-chay-tron-khoi-barca-180-191966.html\" target=\"_blank\">ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dembele s\u1ebd chia tay Barca</span>. Anh c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1nh Malcom h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dembele ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dembele ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/dembele-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ousmane Dembele t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Ba v\u1eeba qua, c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Dembele v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Arsenal s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc 8.9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Dembele. N\u1ebfu ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd mua \u0111\u1ee9t anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng theo t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo, Dembele \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Josep Maria Bartomeu c\u1ee7a Barca. V\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Camp Nou th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Dembele \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal sau khi c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i \u0103n t\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u00e0 Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang v\u00e0 Henrikh Mkhitaryan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-chi-tiet-hop-dong-courtois-sap-ky-voi-real-madrid-172-194030.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Chi ti\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Courtois s\u1eafp k\u00fd v\u1edbi Real Madrid?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-va-giroud-muon-chelsea-mua-nabil-fekir-172-194029.html\">Hazard v\u00e0 Giroud mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2136","checkdouble":"194031"},{"date":"15:20 08/08","title":"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft: \"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/5/van-quyet-toi-da-no-luc-de-duoc-tham-du-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd Daily Star \u0111\u01b0a tin Man United \u0111ang ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Jordi Alba \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho Luke Shaw.</h2><h2>MU nh\u1eafm Jordi Alba\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jordi Alba\" title=\"Jordi Alba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/17/mu-nham-sao-barca-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU nh\u1eafm h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Jordi Alba thay Luke Shaw</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u01afu ti\u00ean ban \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Man United \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Luke Shaw \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Alex Sandro c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u00e0 Danny Rose c\u1ee7a Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Man \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, t\u1edd Daily Star m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng HLV Mourinho \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/jordi-alba-44444.html\" target=\"_blank\">h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Jordi Alba</span> v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTruy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alba l\u00e0 b\u1edfi v\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbng Pep Guardiola t\u1ea1i Barca. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 hy v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Alba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u00f4ng t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1ch ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Man City.</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Jordi Alba v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5p. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng kh\u00e1 \u00eam \u1ea3 t\u1ea1i Camp Nou. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Barca th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u00e1n \u0111i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng cho Alba l\u00e0 Lucas Digne cho Everton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa Shaw v\u00e0 HLV Mourinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u00e0 Shaw h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a MU trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Luke Shaw th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0ng Mourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n kh\u00e1c. Premier League s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh trong 2 ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o 1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU&nbsp;kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/bayern-khong-muon-mua-ante-rebic-193-194033.html\">M.U \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng trong v\u1ee5 s\u0103n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-va-giroud-muon-chelsea-mua-nabil-fekir-172-194029.html\">Hazard v\u00e0 Giroud mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2135","checkdouble":"194032"},{"date":"15:25 08/08","title":"M.U \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng trong v\u1ee5 s\u0103n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/bayern-khong-muon-mua-ante-rebic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho Man United s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U t\u00ednh mua Rebic</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Ante Rebic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Croatia ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t. Anh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Balkan l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRebic mang nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u1ea1y hai c\u00e1nh t\u1edbi trung phong. S\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn 24 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 x\u1eed l\u00fd tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/bayern-khong-muon-mua-ante-rebic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rebic ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t m\u00e0 HLV Jose Mourinho c\u1ee7a Man United \u01b0a th\u00edch. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 c\u00f3 tin Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean r\u00fat lui</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAi c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 Bayern Munich s\u1ebd nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Ante Rebic v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 HLV Niko Kovac, th\u1ea7y c\u0169 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i Eintracht Frankfurt. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u00f4ng qua ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Bayern, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Rebic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-du-dinh-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-rebic-172-192000.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/mu-du-dinh-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-rebic.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-du-dinh-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-rebic-172-192000.html\">MU d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao Croatia</span><br>\r\n<span>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic c\u1ee7a Eintracht Frankfurt, theo Sport Bild, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec gi\u1eefa Bayern v\u00e0 Ante Rebic&rdquo;, Kovac n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sport Bild. &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec trong chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u00f4m nay kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y mai c\u0169ng v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 tin vui v\u1edbi M.U. HLV Mourinho c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. M.U t\u1eebng nh\u1eafm Gareth Bale c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u00e0 Ivan Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan song kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-khung-bayern-chinh-thuc-tu-choi-man-united-172-194011.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-da-dong-y-ban-trung-ve-khung-cho-mu-172-193988.html\">Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng cho M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cuc-lon-cho-thay-mu-chuan-bi-don-trung-ve-moi-172-193882.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho th\u1ea5y M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-dua-ra-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-barca-172-193877.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho M.U, Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-boateng-voi-mu-172-193871.html\">Arsenal gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2134","checkdouble":"194033"},{"date":"15:44 08/08","title":"\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0\" \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Park Hang Seo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/nguoi-nha-ung-ho-quyet-dinh-lua-chon-van-quyet-cua-park-hang-seo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u2013 HLV Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nV\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c &ldquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0&rdquo; tin t\u01b0\u1edfng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft. \u00dd ki\u1ebfn n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u, r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 qua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;N\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea9ng c\u1ea5p. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i, l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1ea1y b\u00e9n. V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Uzbekistan l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t r\u1ed3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn to\u00e0n th\u1ec3, tr\u00e1nh phi\u1ebfn di\u1ec7n. Danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn 3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u01a1n tu\u1ed5i, V\u0103n L\u00e2m c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u0169ng v\u1eady. M\u1ed7i m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u, v\u00e0 HLV s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn m\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/nguoi-nha-ung-ho-quyet-dinh-lua-chon-van-quyet-cua-park-hang-seo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u00d4ng Park \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u00f4ng \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1edf. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, ASIAD c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a di\u1ec5n ra, sao c\u1ee9 l\u00f4i V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ra tranh c\u00e3i? CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1edfi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn h\u1ecd th\u00ec ch\u1ecdn ai b\u00e2y gi\u1edd? Hi\u1ec7n nay HAGL, Viettel hay SLNA kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng Park kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn danh s\u00e1ch.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;D\u00f9 sao, vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 theo b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai. \u00d4ng Park l\u00e0 HLV \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 l\u00fd do c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1ec1 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb x\u01b0a nay, qua bao \u0111\u1eddi HLV r\u1ed3i. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y danh s\u00e1ch 20 ng\u01b0\u1eddi cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u00fang ta \u00edt nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad-472-194022.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad-472-194022.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi ASIAD</span><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng bongda24h t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi-168-193982.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi-168-193982.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, g\u1ea1t V\u0103n L\u00e2m: L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn?</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang b\u00e0n t\u00e1n x\u00f4n xao v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic c\u1ee7a HLV...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/van-quyet-toi-da-no-luc-de-duoc-tham-du-asiad-472-194032.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/5/van-quyet-toi-da-no-luc-de-duoc-tham-du-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/van-quyet-toi-da-no-luc-de-duoc-tham-du-asiad-472-194032.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft: T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD</span><br>\r\nQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh V\u0103n L\u00e2m thay v\u00ec V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 tranh c\u00e3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft chia s\u1ebb sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2133","checkdouble":"194036"}]}